-7694-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7694-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7694-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7694-270x180.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7694.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7704-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7704-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7704-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7704-270x180.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7704.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7705-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7705-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7705-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7705-270x180.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7705.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7550-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7550-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7550-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7550-270x180.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/UV-7550.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="